item.title: Help on adding theiving stalls on a 525 - Mod John R (URGENT)
item.dc:creator: @QuestMaster_2K10 QuestMaster 2K10
item.description:
@QuestMaster_2K10 wrote:

Well, I don’t code 525s, but from experience with Java, click on the Stall you want to add thieving to. With any luck, a message to the command prompt will say “Unhandled Object” blah blah, and say the ObjectID. Then go to whatever class that the Second Options on Objects can be handled in, and use the Case Label, and the Object ID, and use your Code within the Case, and close it using a [b]break;]/b].
